languages.text:
At the end of the Overseer's turn, the Cyber-Eagle ascends and immediately leaves the battlefield. This action doesn’t provoke attacks of opportunity if enemies are present near the Cyber-Eagle during the ability activation.
While {g|f:ec56854df2e84ef196a49079a43b5211}Ascended{/g}, the Cyber-Eagle restores 10% Wounds each round and unlocks more powerful versions of its abilities that the Overseer can use.
